(319, 6, '2015-12-23 10:21:35', 'Waleed', 'Abbas', 'Anjum', 334, '+92-331-5679499', '', 'Dhoke Dandi, Padshahan, Chakwal\nPakistan', '', 'email', 'Omer Adil & Co. Chartered Accountants', 'Audit and Accounts Trainee', 'azn_21_25000', 'azn_26_30000', 'ACCA', 'CAT', '/data/bakertilly/public_html/uploads/Anjum-Updated.docx', '1992-04-29 00:00:00', 'male', 'Pakistani', 'Asian_or_Asian_British_-_Pakistani', 'No', 'yes', '2015-12-23 10:21:35', '0', 'An ACCA Accountancy professional having Experience more then 15 months in my field.\nCurrently working in an Audit and accountancy firm, before this I worked with top cellular operator of Pakistan.\nStrongly organized, passionate and skilled person having great knowledge and experience in IFRS, IASs and ISAs backed by different accounting softwares.', 0, ''),
(320, 1, '2016-01-05 02:09:06', 'IBRAHIM', '', 'AGHAYEV', 335, '+994557905115', '+994124887428', 'Balakishiyev 57', '', 'mobile_anytime', 'Azerbaijan Republic Ministry of Health Analytic Expertise Center', 'Accountant', 'azn_6_10000', 'azn_11_15000', 'part_qualified_ACCA, Other', 'part-qualified CIMA', '/data/bakertilly/public_html/uploads/CV_Ibrahiim_Aghayev.pdf', '1970-01-01 00:00:00', 'male', 'Azerbaijan', 'Not_disclosed', 'none', '', '2016-01-05 02:09:06', '0', 'I believe I have the necessary skills and experience you are seeking and would make a valuable addition to your company.\nAs my resume indicates, I possess more than 7 years of progressive experience in the finance and accounting field.  My professional history includes positions such as Accountant at Analytic Expertise Center of Ministry of Health of Azerbaijan Republic as well as Accountant and Cashier at GEN-LAB LLC.\nMy recent job matches the qualifications you are seeking.  As the Accountant, my responsibilities included bulk of responsibilities which are similar to ones stated in job posting. My supervisor also relied on my ability to Calculation of tax liabilities of clients; Preparation of tax returns and reports to other authorities (social insurance, statistics and employment fund); Bookkeeping of clients; Processing transactions in relevant software applications and others', 0, ''),
(321, 1, '2016-01-13 15:18:01', 'Rufat', '', 'Hajiyev', 336, '+994502542272', '', '', '', 'mobile_anytime', 'Ministry of Taxes of Azerbaijan', 'Senior tax inspector', 'azn_16_20000', 'azn_16_20000', 'part_qualified_ACCA', '', '/data/bakertilly/public_html/uploads/Rufat_Hajiyev_CV.pdf', '1985-08-16 00:00:00', 'male', 'Azerbaijan', 'none', 'No', '', '2016-01-13 15:18:01', '0', 'I have been working in the Ministry of Taxes of the Republic of Azerbaijan for the last 7 years and have an experience in various fields of tax administration. I have a good knowledge on administration of taxation issues of PSAs signed by the Azerbaijani Government and Contractor parties. By 2018, I am planning to become a holder of  Advanced Diploma in International Taxation.', 0, ''),
(322, 6, '2016-01-29 22:36:46', 'Salman', '', 'Khan', 337, '+92 341 9551841', '', 'Village Shalbandi dissitt Burner Kpk pakistan', '', 'email', 'ICMS education system Peshawar Pakistan', 'Accounts and finance officer', 'lt_6000', 'lt_6000', 'ACCA', '', '/data/bakertilly/public_html/uploads/Salman_CV_two_years.docx', '1970-01-01 00:00:00', 'male', 'Pakistani', 'Asian_or_Asian_British_-_Pakistani', 'No', '', '2016-01-29 22:36:46', '0', 'Diligent and enthusiastic with two years of professional exeeience in accounts and finance in three different organisations.\nGood communication and influence skills. Self-starter with excellent analytical, organizational, and time-management skills. A talent for developing and simplifying procedures, and finding innovative solutions. Committed to the highest levels of professional and personal excellence. Able to deal equally well with personnel of all kinds of nationalities in positions from unskilled labour to senior management and work in dynamic and challenging environment.', 0, ''),
(323, 2, '2016-02-20 14:26:09', 'Jeyhun', '', 'Ismayilov', 338, '0502541737', '+994502541737', 'Baku, R.Ismayilov 10 home 49', 'AZ1117', 'email', 'Ministry of Taxes', 'International Relations and tax monitorinf in finance institution', 'lt_6000', 'lt_6000', '', '', '/data/bakertilly/public_html/uploads/CV_Eng.docx', '1987-06-20 00:00:00', 'male', 'Azerbaijan', 'White', 'No', '', '2016-02-20 14:26:09', '0', 'Dear Sir/Madam,\n\nMy first job responsibility was to interpret tax legislation and administration to the large taxpayers and legal entities dealing with PSA. Drafting applications on Double Taxation Treaties was one of my main duties. My second job responsibility was to conduct desk audit for companies specially operating under PSA. At my third post as a senior state tax inspector at International treaties division I carried out relevant activities on preparation of drafts of international agreements signed between the Republic of Azerbaijan and other states on tax matters. I was also dealing with international taxation issues, including transfer pricing, BEPS, FATCA, OECD - Global Forum (peer-review).   \nI have been working at International Practices and Innovations division of MOT. \n', 0, ''),
