(327, 2, '2016-04-07 00:19:58', 'Esmiralda', '', 'Shirinova', 342, '+44 7599 474476', '+99412 5109188', '', '', 'email', 'AFB BANK', 'Intern in IT department', 'lt_6000', 'lt_6000', '', '', '/data/bakertilly/public_html/uploads/CV8.pdf', '1998-02-13 00:00:00', 'female', 'Azerbaijan', 'White', 'No', 'no', '2016-04-07 00:19:58', '0', 'Dear Sir or Madam,\n\nI am looking for summer internship opportunities in IT industry and very interested in IT area and how is it applied to business. I am a first year student in the University of Southampton, pursuing a bachelor’s degree in Information Technology in Organizations. I am confident that my experiences, skills and strong interest have prepared me to be a good intern for your company, also helping me to gain more knowledge in IT and business. My experience as an intern in “AFB BANK” in Baku makes me more courageous as I already know how to be useful for an organization, while trying to get the most of new knowledge from experienced people.\nI  would like the opportunity to meet with you to discuss any internship opportunities you might have. Thank you for your time and consideration.\n\nSincerely.\nEsmiralda Shirinova', 0, ''),
