(370, 9, '2017-01-16 17:14:09', 'Orkhan', 'Yusibov', 'Aydin', 386, '0507765086', '', '', '', 'none', 'Bank VTB Azerbaijan', 'Head of Financial Analysis Division', 'lt_6000', 'lt_6000', 'Other', 'CFA', '/data/bakertilly/public_html/uploads/CV-Orkhan_Yusibov.pdf', '1990-02-01 00:00:00', 'male', 'Azerbaijan', 'Not_disclosed', 'No', '', '2017-01-16 17:14:09', '0', 'Currently, I am a Head of Financial Analysis Division in Bank VTB (Azerbaijan), subsidiary bank of one of the global provider of financial services. My professional career at Bank VTB (Azerbaijan) started almost two and half years ago as a specialist in Financial Analyst and Budget Planning department. \nI have a Master of Science degree at University of Essex, one of the Europe’s leading economics department, specialization in Financial Economics. I am also a CFA level 3 candidate. \nI always have a passion to improve myself and enjoy working in a team with people who have innovative ideas and strategic approach to work. I am fluent in 4 languages: English, Russian, Azerbaijani, Turkish. \n\nI would appreciate the opportunity to have an interview in one of the most prestigious accounting and business advisory firms for the before mentioned position.', 0, ''),
(371, 8, '2017-02-09 11:27:42', 'Orkhan', '', 'Mammadov', 387, '050-386-20-02', '012-349-00-94', 'Xirdalan', 'AZ0100', 'email', 'AZERSU OJSC', 'Lead tax expert', 'azn_16_20000', 'none', 'part_qualified_ACCA', 'DipIFR', '/data/bakertilly/public_html/uploads/NEW_CV_2_son.pdf', '1989-02-08 00:00:00', 'male', 'Azerbaijan', 'none', 'No', 'no', '2017-02-09 11:27:42', '0', 'I was the most experienced tax economist in Azersu. I handled all tax relations and statements. I know, I\'m late, but if you give me a chance, I won\'t let you down.', 0, ''),
