(374, 9, '2017-05-09 15:53:36', 'Gunel', '', 'Aliyeva', 390, '0552078858', '0123714684', 'Baku. 35 Gandja avenue. Range 78', '', 'email', 'I didn\'t work', 'I didn\'t work', 'lt_6000', 'lt_6000', '', '', '/data/bakertilly/public_html/uploads/Gunels_Résumé_(2).pdf', '1990-09-14 00:00:00', 'female', 'Azerbaijan', 'White', 'No', '', '2017-05-09 15:53:36', '0', 'I can adapt quickly to people.My motivation depends on my work.If I am lucky in my work, my motivation will increase.And I will do my next work better than last.My strengths is firstly I am very patiently.And If I have a goal in my job, I will reach it soon.Unfortunately,I didn\'t work until now.But I would like to work with you not for salary,but for experience and career.', 0, ''),
