(376, 9, '2017-05-29 19:57:47', 'Nijat', '', 'Mutallimov', 392, '+994556454907', '', '', '', 'mobile_anytime', 'YapiKredi Bank Azerbaijan', 'Credit Underwriting Specialist', 'azn_11_15000', 'azn_11_15000', '', '', '/data/bakertilly/public_html/uploads/CV_(Nijat_Mutallimov).pdf', '1990-02-17 00:00:00', 'male', 'Azerbaijan', 'White', 'No', 'no', '2017-05-29 19:57:47', '0', 'During my graduate studies I have demonstrated strong academic performance in all courses, maintaining a 3.65 CGPA. The courses I have completed have given me a solid foundation in the tools, processes and methodologies involved in the successful Financial Analysis. These courses are consisting of Financial Management, Fixed Income Analysis, Financial Derivatives, Investment Management which capture the corporate side of finance and the courses like Financial Economics, Time Series Applied to Finance, Probability Theory, Stochastic Calculus for Finance which grab quantitative part of finance. When it comes to soft skills I have a proven ability to learn challenging concepts quickly and have developed my competencies in diverse areas. These abilities directed me to the following awards and scholarships:\n- Full Scholarship by Azerbaijan State covering the studies towards the MSc. degree at the METU (2014) \n- 2017 CFA Program Access Scholarship (2016).', 0, ''),
