(249, 'en', 1, 107, 1, '2013-07-02 00:40:38', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Partner', '<p>Ziya Ibrahimov started as an Audit Manager at Baker Tilly Azerbaijan responsible for financial services industry practice in December 2007 and later in October 2008 he has been promoted to a director of audit and assurance department. In 2011, he has been assigned to a new role as an audit partner in the firm. Ziya has graduated from the Midwestern State University Graduate School (Texas, USA) with MBA degree in 2002 and joined PricewaterhouseCoopers international audit firm in 2003 and has worked from associate to Assistant Manager till December 2007. In March 2007 he has became a member of internationally recognized accounting association ACCA. From 2003 to 2007 Ziya has participated in different projects within CIS, in particularly in Georgia, Russia and Ukraine. Ziya has extensive exposure on IFRS audits of banking, insurance, leasing, telecommunication and retail industries.<br></p>', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null'),
(250, 'en', 1, 108, 1, '2013-07-02 00:43:57', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Deputy Partner', '<p>Narmin Hajiyeva is a Deputy Partner/Tax and Legal Services at Baker Tilly Azerbaijan since March 2017. Narmin has graduated from Kings College London (KCL) with LLM degree on International Business Law in 2011. Narmin started her career as a lawyer at Legal Department of the Ministry of Taxes of the Republic of Azerbaijan and has been promoted to the Head of Tax Policy Department. During the years at the Ministry of Taxes Narmin dealt with complicated taxation issues and led the Secretariat of Appeal Council of the Ministry. She has participated in many projects including amendments to Tax Code, as well as Civil Code of the Republic of Azerbaijan. She also attended many conferences on taxation, international taxation organized by OECD, IOTA, IMF and tax administrations of foreign countries.<br></p>', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null'),
(270, 'en', 1, 120, 1, '2013-09-18 23:41:40', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '​Audit Manager', '<p>He graduated from the faculty of Economics and Administrative Sciences of the Bosphorus University in Istanbul in 2007. Immediately after graduation, Azad started his audit career in KPMG. Since then he worked in KPMG offices of Istanbul, Moscow and Hong Kong for approximately one, four, and one and a half years respectively. Along with the strong background in such industries as Oil&amp;Gas, Commercial&amp;Consumer Markets and Industrial Markets, Azad has experience in advisory services related to IPO. Azad is currently undergoing the final stage of his ACCA qualification.<br></p>', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null'),
(251, 'en', 1, 109, 1, '2013-07-02 00:44:28', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '​Financial Advisory Services Manager', '<p>Vadim Abdullayev graduated from Azerbaijan State Economic University with the bachelor degree in financial management. He started as a Financial Advisory Services Executive at Baker Tilly Azerbaijan in June 2008. In 2010, he has been promoted to Financial Advisory Manager position – one of the leading this line of the company’s services. Vadim possesses strong background in audit and financial advisory of the energy, communication and construction sector companies. He spent almost 4 years in PWC on the role of associate and senior associate participating in audit and financial advisory engagement in the Azerbaijan Republic, the Russian Federation, Ukraine, Kazakhstan and the Republic of Georgia. During this time, he participated in the number of audit, due diligence and advisory projects of companies operating in financial services, energy, mining, telecommunication, and hospitality and retail sectors. Vadim is currently working on his CFA (Chartered Financial Analyst) qualification.<br></p>', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null'),
(252, 'en', 1, 110, 1, '2013-07-02 00:45:00', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '​Audit Partner', '<p>Rustam Safaraliyev started as an Audit Manager at Baker Tilly Azerbaijan responsible for oil and gas industry practice in August 2009 and from October 2010 is a director of audit and assurance department. He has a strong background in audit of energy, manufacturing, service and finance companies. Rustam has graduated from Azerbaijan State Economics University with bachelor degree in business administration, first alumni of Special Talented Groups and master degree in International Economic Relations. He also obtained statutory audit license in 2008. Rustam has started his audit career in Deloitte in 2005 and has worked from associate to experienced senior till July 2009. In August 2010 he has became a member of internationally recognized accounting association ACCA. He has participated in the audit projects in Azerbaijan as well as outside of the countries such as Russia, Kazakhstan, Georgia.</p>', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null'),
(23, 'en', 1, 3, 1, '2013-01-23 00:12:59', 'Services', 'Services', 'Services', '<p>Services</p>\n', '<p>Services</p>\n', '<p>Services</p>\n', '<p>Services</p>\n', '<p>Services</p>\n', '<p>Services</p>\n', 1, '', 12, 0, 'Koala8.jpg', 'Koala9.jpg', 'Koala10.jpg', 'Koala11.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'null', 'Baker Tilly Azerbaijan provides a range of accountancy and business advisory services to assist you with a full spectrum of advice from compliance to facilitating growth. <br><br>Our teams of specialists bring a wide range of experience in a variety of disciplines, with industry specific knowledge of the latest practices and emerging issues. <br><br>Whether serving public sector organizations, owner managed businesses, private individuals or listed companies with overseas operations, our goal is to help our clients achieve their ambitions.<br><br>We stay closely attuned to all our clients\' varying needs and aspirations, working in partnership to help transform their vision into reality.', '​An audit is more than a formality; it is a necessity to protect your business and encourage it to thrive. Early warnings, open communication and pragmatic resolution of issues are the essential features of our approach.', '​Baker Tilly Azerbaijan has an in-depth expertise in the fields of corporate finance. We do have specialized skills in multiple lines of service and industry. The team work and the sharing of knowledge assure our high quality standards and an increased value to our clients.', '​A Consultant of Baker Tilly Azerbaijan never gives advice, he/she transfers knowledge and does everything possible to keep the mutual competence, which we have gained as an integral part of your organization for years to come.', '​Baker Tilly Azerbaijan provides independent forensic services to businesses with exposures that include business disputes, investigations, asset tracing, embezzlement, and allegations of financial malfeasance.', '​\'Profit improvement\' is a key component in Baker Tilly Azerbaijan’s Growth Programme, a structured approach that looks at the fundamental business criteria used by banks, venture capitalists and other financiers to assess proposals.', 'During tough times operating profitably in diverse markets is essential to the success of businesses – not only for survival but in order to thrive and flourish. It’s important then, to be able to manage operations across international boundaries making the most of the opportunities available to you.', '​Many businesses are beginning to recognize that their information systems and financial processes have not kept pace with their growth. As a result, management and executives are not equipped with the critical business intelligence that is needed to make timely decisions in a complex regulatory environment.', '​Outsourcing has long been a key to success in the corporate world. Outsourcing services offered by Baker Tilly Azerbaijan allows you to focus on the core strategic activities of your business, while our accounting professionals take care of the challenging task of running your accounting functions.', 'Baker Tilly Azerbaijan can offer a fully comprehensive payroll service unique to each client\'s individual needs. We assure all of our clients’ services with the greatest of care, continual development of knowledge of payroll processes and regulations, and with state-of-the-art IT tools tailored to varying customer needs.', '​At Baker Tilly Azerbaijan, we focus on your specific needs with a full range of accounting and advisory services. Our professionals connect with your specific targets and expectations to deliver the right solutions, consistently and proactively.', '​For a commercial enterprise, or any other type of organization, surviving financial difficulty is a careful step-by-step process best negotiated with the help of specialist accountants and recovery experts.', '​​When it comes to tax planning, clients need more than technical guidance from their service advisors. They need a firm that combines technical knowledge with a personal commitment to client service and a unique understanding of client needs.', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null'),
(24, 'en', 1, 4, 1, '2013-01-23 00:13:14', 'Support', 'Support', 'Support', '<p>Support</p>\n', '<p>Support</p>\n', '<p>Support</p>\n', '<p>Support</p>\n', '<p>Support</p>\n', '<p>Support</p>\n', 1, '', 99, 0, 'Koala12.jpg', 'Koala13.jpg', 'Koala14.jpg', 'Koala15.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'null', 'Baker Tilly Azerbaijan provides special Consulting Services for a range of sectors. With a personal, partner-led approach, we work as a trusted adviser to a wealth of clients. We\'re dedicated to the needs of specific sectors. By focusing closely on each sector\'s unique influences we are able to help you achieve your objectives through providing accurate, informed and appropriate advice.', 'We can construct a plan for the future to meet your particular goals by asking the right questions and assessing your current situation.', 'By reviewing your business strategy we can help you improve your profits and managing risk more effectively.', 'As Baker Tilly Azerbaijan we do have prominent experience collaborating with Banks in Azerbaijan. We do understand business needs and our professional team will support your companies successfully.', 'We have wide experience of working with clients in the energy and natural resources sector including international companies with operations throughout the world.', 'Financial services authorized businesses have faced many changes in recent years and the future will be equally challenging with continuing regulatory developments. We have a team of financial services experts with a deep knowledge of the issues facing businesses in this environment.', 'From producers to consumers we work throughout the supply chain and understand how issues can impact the whole sector.', 'We provide compliance and business advisory services to privately owned, private equity backed and quoted Azerbaijani companies across various segments of manufacturing sector.', 'At Baker Tilly Azerbaijan we are extremely proud of the fact that our non-profits team has established a strong presence within the sector.', '​The development of long-term relationships with our clients enables us to understand your business requirements and provide the appropriate advice.', '​Baker Tilly Azerbaijan\'s dedicated team in the retail sector have significant experience of delivering focused, practical and up-to-the-minute advice that improves the performance of our clients\' businesses.', '​Azerbaijani telecommunications sector is the second largest recipient of foreign investment after oil and gas industry. Since Azerbaijan pays attention to Telecommunication and IT Sector intensively, we cooperate with our clients successfully.', '​​We work with a significant number of clients across the full spectrum of the tourism and hospitality sector.', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null'),
(25, 'en', 1, 5, 1, '2013-01-23 00:12:32', 'Partners', 'Partners', 'Partners', '<p>Partners</p>\n', '<p>Partners</p>\n', '<p>Partners</p>\n', '<p>Partners</p>\n', '<p>Partners</p>\n', '<p>Partners</p>\n', 1, '', 6, 0, 'Koala16.jpg', 'Koala17.jpg', 'Koala18.jpg', 'Koala19.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Case studies', '<p class=\"intro\">The solutions and advice we offer our clients are focussed on helping them achieve their objectives.</p><p>The case studies available in this section are just a handful of work we have carried out.</p>', 'Featured case studies', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
