(96, 'en', 1, 53, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Profit improvement', '<p><font class=\"intro\">Income, available funds and ultimately some form of profit – these are essential if an organisation is to pursue its objectives, lower risk and meet the aspirations of stakeholders.</font>&nbsp;<br><br>For an enterprise to be sustainable, it must be capable of generating and controlling cash flow to create a surplus.<br>&nbsp;<br>Baker Tilly\'s profit advisers can work with you to make a detailed review of cash and profits in your business, considering each component and its impact on the company\'s progress.<br>&nbsp;<br>We\'ll help you to refresh your business model, test key assumptions and seek opportunities for profit improvement through:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">refinement of existing processes</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">exploring ways to win more new business</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">looking for repositioning opportunities</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">reducing overhead</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">adding value between products and services</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">improving operating efficiency.</li></ul><p>\'Profit improvement\' is a key component in the Baker Tilly Growth Programme, a structured approach that looks at the fundamental business criteria used by banks, venture capitalists and other financiers to assess proposals.</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(97, 'en', 1, 54, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Risk management', '<p><font class=\"intro\" style=\"line-height: normal; \">Risk management is integral to good governance and successful development.</font><br><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Every type of enterprise entails risk and those who manage risk most effectively can gain competitive advantage – it\'s as much about seeking opportunities as it is about being cautious or defensive.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Think ahead, be prepared and move when the time is right.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Baker Tilly\'s risk advisers can work with you to support your need for effective risk management in the strategic development of your organisation.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">We will address with you questions of strategic focus, positioning, legal and regulatory issues, risk tolerance and appetite, mitigation options, controls and contingencies and what actions and commitments are needed from your people.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">\'Risk management\' is a key component in the Baker Tilly Growth Programme, a structured approach that looks at the fundamental business criteria used by banks, venture capitalists and other financiers to assess proposals.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">As well as advising the commercial sector, particularly companies with AIM and growth aspirations, we have also developed specific risk management processes tailored for pension scheme trustees and professional practices.</span><br></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(98, 'en', 1, 55, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Strategic development', '<p><font class=\"intro\">Define your success - how will you recognise it? Are you headed in the right direction? Are you actually making the progress you want?</font>&nbsp;<br><br>Baker Tilly\'s strategic development advisers have the breadth and depth of experience to work with you to refresh and clarify your strategy and by so doing ensure the alignment of your top management team. This is never more important than in the run-up to market flotation.<br>&nbsp;<br>We will explore with you key objectives and plans:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Do your objectives reflect what you really want for your business?</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Do your plans anticipate the need for managing&nbsp; change?</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Do all the key decision makers want the same outcomes?</li></ul><p>With you we will look at current and future products and services, roles and structure, your people and your market focus.<br>&nbsp;<br>We will help you establish progress indicators and an implementation process to generate and maintain momentum.<br>&nbsp;<br>Most plans fail, not because they are not good plans, but because they are not fully implemented. We will coach you through this.<br>&nbsp;<br>\'Strategic development\' is a key component in the Baker Tilly Growth Programme, a structured approach that looks at the fundamental business criteria used by banks, venture capitalists and other financiers to assess proposals.</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(99, 'en', 1, 56, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Team strategic development', '<p><font class=\"intro\" style=\"line-height: normal; \">Good people are an organisation\'s greatest asset. Moulding your people into a strong unit can result in a team that is greater than the sum of its parts.</font><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Having the right people is crucial to running a successful business; ultimately investors and financiers will decide whether or not to support a proposal based on their confidence in the team\'s ability to deliver.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Our experienced business advisers will work with you, your management and key personnel, to ensure that the thinking, activities and operating decisions are all aligned with the company\'s objectives and strategic goals.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">The benefits of this process are clear purpose and motivation. Your people will feel more involved with the strategy, better focused on their contribution, coordinated with the contribution of others and generally more inspired about the team\'s relevance to the organisation\'s success.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">\'Team development\' is a key component in the Baker Tilly Growth Programme, a structured approach that looks at the fundamental business criteria used by banks, venture capitalists and other financiers to assess proposals.&nbsp;</span>​<br></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(100, 'en', 1, 57, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Wealth tracker', '<p><font class=\"intro\" style=\"line-height: normal; \">At any stage of a career or business, increasing and protecting your financial assets is essential if you want to ensure personal rewards and a secure future.</font><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">However, a well thought out strategy for managing personal wealth and its ongoing success is easy to neglect for the driven, career-focused individual.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Baker Tilly will help you to assess your current position, establish your priorities and establish a structured plan to control and develop the wealth you create.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Our wealth tracker has consistently enabled our clients to clarify their key objectives and produce core strategies that align all elements of their personal capital.</span><br></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(101, 'en', 1, 58, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Commercial insurance', '<p class=\"intro\">Our comprehensive range of insurance broking services is designed to meet a variety of business requirements. These extend from the protection of tangible assets such as buildings, contents and computer equipment to professional indemnity and insurance against loss of profits or income.</p><p>Understanding that every business has different requirements is essential. We have a host of insurance solutions and risk management services available for our clients, including:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Insurance programme design, advice and implementation, ranging from basic requirements tailored to meet your needs through to in depth analysis and placement of complex, multi national strategies</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Independent, expert advice and assistance on claims</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Advice on the importance of and implementation of Risk Management procedures.</li></ul><p>Our promise is that we will match your very specific and unique risks to the most appropriate insurers, obtaining the optimum cover and an economic premium.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>At Baker Tilly Insurance Services, our knowledge and expertise means we can arrange some of the most comprehensive and beneficial insurance packages available in the marketplace.</p><p>Our specialist areas include:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Commercial property</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Professional indemnity</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Liability</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Media</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Education</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Charities</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Marine, freight and logistics</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Care sector</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Insurance due diligence</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Trade associations &amp; membership bodies</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Wholesale insurance</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Professional connections</li></ul><h2>Contact</h2><p>Heather Evans<br>T: 01442 860812<br>Email:&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href=\"mailto:heather.evans@bakertillyinsurance.co.uk\" href=\"mailto:heather.evans@bakertillyinsurance.co.uk\">heather.evans@bakertillyinsurance.co.uk</a></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(102, 'en', 1, 59, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CompleteHR', '<p><font class=\"”intro”\" size=\"”+0\" style=\"line-height: normal; \">In 2010/11, over 200,000 claims were submitted to Industrial Tribunals by aggrieved employees. This was a 56% increase in claims compared to the previous year.&nbsp;</font><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">We expect the above figures to increase over time and with significant damages being awarded in many cases. Accordingly, Baker Tilly Insurance Services (BTIS) has researched and developed a solution for employers that encompasses qualified legal advice for employment disputes, supported by an insurance product to support any legal costs and/or awards incurred in the process.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">The solution is provided in conjunction with one of Europe’s leading commercial insurers, AXA and a panel of law firms (including a number of the UKs largest firms).</span></p><p><strong>How the cover works&nbsp;</strong><br><br>The cover focuses on the issues and factors in a business which can lead to Employment Tribunal claims and offers sound practical and commercial advice on their prevention before they become a serious problem. In addition, it offers financial protection against the costs associated with defending a full range of employment claims from unfair dismissal to discrimination.</p><p><strong>The benefits&nbsp;</strong><br><br>The overall service is tailored to each individual client’s specific needs and different levels of service are available. Although this approach is flexible, there are core areas of service provided, including:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Employment advice - a dedicated client legal team to advise on all employment law issues and to identify solutions that are legal and commercially practical</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Online information and resources - clients will have access to documents, procedures and template letters that accord with HR best practice</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Protecting profits - providing cover to fund for awards and compensation payments awarded (subject to maximum limits), decided by a tribunal in the circumstances of an unfair dismissal finding or a finding of unlawful discrimination.</li></ul><p><strong>Key features of insurance cover&nbsp;</strong><br><br>The wide ranging cover includes:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Any one claim cover</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">An excess of £2500 that would reduce to £NIL should the client buy HR Insurance cover and follow the solicitor’s advice</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Very competitive premiums</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Additional Directors’ and Officers’, Entity and Fidelity covers available.</li></ul><p><strong>Summary&nbsp;</strong><br><br>We consider this scheme to be unique in that as long as the solicitor’s advice is followed, it will pay claims where others do not. Other legal expenses and Employment Practices Liability Insurance products have limitations and will not usually consider claims unless there is more than a 51% chance of a successful defence. This means our partner solicitor is able to provide clients with genuinely commercial advice, not overshadowed by a third party’s best interest.</p><h2>Contact us</h2><p>Paul Winterbottom ACII<br>T: 0161 972 2423<br>Email:&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href=\"mailto:paul.winterbottom@bakertillyinsurance.co.uk\" href=\"mailto:paul.winterbottom@bakertillyinsurance.co.uk\">paul.winterbottom@bakertillyinsurance.co.uk</a></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(103, 'en', 1, 60, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Personal lines insurance', '<p class=\"intro\"><font class=\"”intro”\" size=\"”+0\">We understand discerning clients and have a depth and breadth of knowledge and experience. We are professionals who genuinely understand the true nature of your insurance requirements and provide a tailored solution to suit your needs.</font></p><h2>Our insurance solutions</h2><p>We understand that with period properties, antiques and other high value items it is of paramount importance that your specific needs are catered for and in the event of a claim, the restoration, repair or replacement is undertaken by a specialist.</p><p>Our solutions offer wide ranging cover and a claims service that allows our clients to use their preferred suppliers and contractors.</p><p>Some of the insurers we use will provide free valuations for buildings, contents and fine art.</p><p>We understand that with the pressures and pace of modern life, it is sometimes easy to overlook security e.g. forget to set your alarm. We are often able to arrange policies which are not subject to alarm conditions.</p><p>In addition we can offer access to security specialists and provide advice and guidance on security measures. Sometimes simple solutions such as videoing / photographing your valuables and storing these securely away from your home can facilitate a speedy and fair claims process.</p><p>Our solutions can include extra covers such as Identity Fraud, Legal Expenses and Travel Insurance.</p><p>Our clients have direct access to our insurance specialists and will be given a primary contact to deal with on a day to day basis. In addition, our clients have access to the directors of the company who maintain a close involvement in the day to day management of the business.</p><h2>What we can insure:</h2><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Buildings including period and thatched properties&nbsp;</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Contents including antiques and fine art</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Holiday homes both in the UK and abroad</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Motor including classic cars</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Yachts and motor boats</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Private aviation</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Investment properties including Holiday Lets</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Travel</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Your children’s personal requirements</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Contact</h2><p>Nina Nash<br>T: 01442 860812<br>Email:&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href=\"mailto:nina.nash@bakertillyinsurance.co.uk\" href=\"mailto:nina.nash@bakertillyinsurance.co.uk\">nina.nash@bakertillyinsurance.co.uk</a></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(104, 'en', 1, 61, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '​Trade associations, membership bodies and trade sectors', '<p><font class=\"”intro”\" size=\"”+0\">Our specialist Schemes Division has many years experience in&nbsp; providing market leading schemes tailored for affinity groups, associations and membership bodies.</font></p><p>At the forefront of the Division’s philosophy is the ability to reintroduce the \'service\' back into a service industry that has distanced itself from the importance of what a knowledgeable and personalised service means to a client. We pride ourselves on a modern service with traditional values.</p><p>By working together in partnership, Baker Tilly Insurance Services and your affinity group or association will protect the members, bring additional values to membership and strengthen member loyalty.&nbsp; In addition, by using the collective buying power from premiums of the well managed member businesses we can keep insurance premiums lower.</p><h2>Trade sectors&nbsp;– Independent retailers</h2><p>This facility is designed for Hardware and DIY stores, Ironmongers, Builders Merchants and Wholesalers.</p><p><strong>Careful consideration has been given to providing exactly the cover the industry requires with benefits including:</strong></p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">a nil glass excess</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">full theft cover, including goods in the open</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">£5,000,000 public liability cover&nbsp;</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">legal expenses cover.<br><em>Quotations, full terms and conditions are available on request.</em></li></ul><p>We have looked closely at the type of insurance cover these sectors require and have produced an insurance package that genuinely provides the protection that today’s professional retailer needs in one document.</p><p>Our facility is placed with a leading market insurer and we have designated loss adjusters who deal with any loss quickly to avoid interruption to the business.</p><p>Discounts are available for memberships of certain trade associations. In addition to cost effective commercial cover, Baker Tilly Insurance Services can also provide advice on motor and other types of insurance to complete the portfolio.</p><p><strong>We have also created and currently manage insurance schemes for the following sectors:</strong></p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Agricultural Machinery Dealers</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Groundcare and Garden Machinery Dealers</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Copy Shops</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Bowls clubs</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Garden Centres and in particular, their Franchises</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Contact</h2><p>Heather Evans<br>T: 01442 860812<br>Email:&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href=\"mailto:heather.evans@bakertillyinsurance.co.uk\" href=\"mailto:heather.evans@bakertillyinsurance.co.uk\">heather.evans@bakertillyinsurance.co.uk</a></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(105, 'en', 1, 62, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'North American business services', '<p class=\"intro\">The Baker Tilly&nbsp;North American desk provides services to UK, European and&nbsp;North American organisations looking at inward and outward investment opportunities.</p><p>Our team has a wealth of experience in both UK and North American accounting and taxation and works closely with our Baker Tilly International member firms in North America to deliver a high quality service to multi-national companies.</p><p>For inward investors we can provide a range of services including:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">company registrations and accounting&nbsp;</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">corporate and employee tax advice and compliance&nbsp;</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">tax structuring&nbsp;</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">transfer pricing&nbsp;</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">VAT services&nbsp;</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">valuations and due diligence&nbsp;</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">audit&nbsp;</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">access to capital markets</li></ul><p>We have successfully taken a number of North American groups onto the Alternative Investment Market (AIM) in the UK and assisted UK companies listing in North America.</p><p>For UK companies seeking to access North American markets to make acquisitions or to obtain access to capital by listing on a US or Canadian exchange, we can assist either directly or through one of our North American member firms.</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(106, 'en', 1, 63, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Israel business services', '<p>The Baker Tilly Israel desk provides advice and practical assistance to UK clients wishing to explore business opportunities in Israel and to companies from Israel wishing to conduct business in the UK.&nbsp; Baker Tilly’s dedicated Israel Group was launched in order to satisfy the demand for specialised advice with teams based in both the UK and Israel.</p><p>Here in the UK, we have considerable experience with Diane Gwilliam, Head of the Israel Group.&nbsp; We also have a number of teams specialising in service streams including tax, transaction support and audit.&nbsp; They can:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">help with the day-to-day practicalities of doing business in Israel with on-going support from our local experts</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">help Israel-based companies aiming to raise funds in the uk through the equity capital markets</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">provide the complete range of tax, advisory and assurance services</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">assist Israel-based companies seeking to gain entry into the uk through organic growth or M&amp;A</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">identify market opportunities and design appropriate market entry strategies based on rigorous assessment</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">use the international network to help clients to identify and establish local partner alliances in Israel or the UK</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">provide commercial and financial due diligence services</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">when planning tax, legal and human resources issues we can advise on government regulations and local requirements</li></ul><p>The members of the Israel Group have considerable experience of working with the teams in Israel and have developed in-depth understanding not only of doing business but of the business culture in modern Israel which can often vary from region to region - making our local knowledge invaluable.</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(107, 'en', 1, 64, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Baker Tilly International', '<p class=\"intro\">Baker Tilly International is a worldwide network of premier accountancy and business advisory firms united by a commitment to provide exceptional client service. 26,000 people in&nbsp;114 countries worldwide share experiences and ideas to help clients meet challenges and proactively respond to opportunities. International capability and global consistency of service are central to the way we work.</p><h3>Size and reach</h3><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">8th largest network in the world by combined revenue</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">147 independent member firms in 114 countries worldwide</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">26,000 people</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">US$3.13bn, the combined revenue of the independent member firms.</li></ul><h3><br></h3><h3>A team approach</h3><p>It is the strong relationship between member firms that&nbsp;is the key factors that enable us to overcome time and cross border complexities to deliver a quality service.</p><p>Our service approach is based around a global lead partner who serves as the single point of contact for a client, irrespective of the size of engagement, co-ordinating all work being carried out by the independent member firms and ensuring it is completed to the highest standards, within budget and deadline. Regional and country lead partners provide local services and the expertise and understanding necessary to navigate the unique dynamics of each of the marketplaces where we do business.</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(108, 'en', 1, 65, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Corporate restructuring', '<p><font class=\"intro\" style=\"line-height: normal; \">The combination of a dip in trading and a gap in cash flow may be enough to cause pressure or even crisis. Whatever the reason, financial distress erodes confidence in the business and shareholder value.</font><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">It is essential to move swiftly and decisively to implement corrective measures – the sooner specialist advice is sought the more likely a recovery can be made.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">If dealt with promptly and intelligently, at the early stages of the decline curve, it\'s possible to maximise recovery opportunities. But neglected or misdiagnosed it could eventually lead to insolvency and failure.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Baker Tilly\'s experts advise boards and other stakeholders (lenders, investor groups, creditors, landlords) on stabilising crisis, turnaround strategy and planned restructure. Our turnaround and restructuring specialists can help you handle some of the tough decisions and negotiations.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">We\'ll make sure all available options for renewing a business and revitalising prospects are considered, including accelerated mergers or acquisitions, providing forecast assurance to external stakeholders where necessary.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Through our Baker Tilly International network we\'re also able to draw upon local knowledge for most assignments that cross borders. Our list of successes includes rescue and restructuring projects around the globe.</span><br></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(109, 'en', 1, 66, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Covenant assessment services', '<p><font class=\"intro\" size=\"+0\" style=\"line-height: normal; \">A pension deficit&nbsp;can present a major obstacle to a company\'s overall health and can also be a sensitive matter that requires discrete expert guidance and experienced negotiation, even more so in the current economic climate.</font><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Our industry award-winning Covenant Assessment Services (CAS) group&nbsp;has UK-wide expertise&nbsp;in&nbsp;supporting trustees and employer companies of&nbsp;defined benefit&nbsp;schemes and provides assistance to them in overcoming difficulties within the complexities of pensions legislation.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Our&nbsp;</span><a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/SiteCollectionDocuments/RR/CAS%20credentials.pdf\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/SiteCollectionDocuments/RR/CAS%20credentials.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"line-height: normal; \">credentials</a><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;(Download PDF 306kb) include acting for £billion-plus multi-employer schemes, through to&nbsp;single employer schemes with assets of £10 million and below. Whatever the scale, the same quality of input and output is assured.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Our CAS group, is an integral part of Baker Tilly’s national leading&nbsp;</span><a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sectors/pensions.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sectors/pensions.aspx\" style=\"line-height: normal; \">Pensions</a><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">group, which draws together our expertise and services in working with the industry from across the firm. In the UK, Baker Tilly acts for more than 1,000 occupational schemes and readily engages with the industry through membership of a number of pensions associations. &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>​<br></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(110, 'en', 1, 67, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Formal insolvency', '<p><font class=\"intro\" style=\"line-height: normal; \">If a business is being pressed by creditors or regulators and correction or restructure are not available options, it\'s essential directors take advice on their position and their obligations under the law.</font><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Not surprisingly, this is unfamiliar territory to many – certainly no one intends to arrive at this position and the realisation can be uncomfortable. But correct action, promptly taken, will help to make the best of any retrievable value in the business and the requisite protection.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">In some cases this can lead to a better outcome than principals and stakeholders might have dared hope for.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Baker Tilly\'s licensed Insolvency Practitioners are knowledgeable and well-versed in the administration of trading bodies and asset protection.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Our negotiation skills and experience in relationship management enable us to deal with all issues when handling the technical aspects of a liquidation or receivership.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">When necessary we can step in at short notice to act as Administrator, Administrative Receiver, Supervisor or Liquidator.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Though the circumstances may be difficult, our professional approach will serve the interests of damage limitation and reconstruction, managing exposure to loss and realising value where possible.</span><br></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(111, 'en', 1, 68, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '​Special investigations and personal insolvency', '<p><font class=\"intro\" style=\"line-height: normal; \">Baker Tilly has a market-leading special investigations team that deals with international asset tracing and contentious insolvencies involving allegations of fraud.</font><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">We can implement formal insolvency procedures to recover monies in the UK and overseas through our network of associates in Baker Tilly International.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">By having the right people working on each aspect of a case we enjoy a good record of success.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">We\'re experienced in handling Individual Voluntary Arrangements (IVAs) and bankruptcies, some of them high-profile cases attracting media attention.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Cases Baker Tilly\'s team investigate include Court appointed Receiverships, Provisional Liquidations, PIU Liquidations, Compulsory Liquidations, Proceeds of Crime Act, Drug Trafficking Act and Criminal Justice Act appointments.</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"line-height: normal; \"><span style=\"line-height: normal; \">Our reputation is for steady, meticulous working, careful attention to detail and technical excellence.</span><br></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '',