ecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Help with business transformations and with&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/finance/mergers-and-acquisitions-and-private-equity.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/finance/mergers-and-acquisitions-and-private-equity.aspx\">raising debt and equity capital</a>&nbsp;through our contacts with venture capital and private equity providers</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Identifying acquisition partners and&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/finance/capital-markets.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/finance/capital-markets.aspx\">advising on exits either through trade sales or flotations</a></li></ul>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(131, 'en', 1, 88, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'null', '<p>Besides other sectors, non-profit sector is highly developed in the country. Various local and international non-governmental organizations, educational institutions, charities and other sosial entites are functioning in Azerbaijan. <br></p><p>At Baker Tilly Azerbaijan we are extremely proud of the fact that our non-profits team has for many years established a leading presence within the sector. <br></p><p>With our professional team and a wide range of advisory services, we are able to deliver innovative and sector leading solutions to our diverse combination of clients, wherever they are based. <br></p><ul><li>Charities, Social Enterprises <br></li><li>Public Sector<br></li><li> Education Institutions<br></li></ul>', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null'),
(132, 'en', 1, 89, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Academies', '<p><font class=\"intro\" size=\"+0\">The Academies sector has become the most dynamic area of education over the last two years.&nbsp;But with new opportunities have come significant risks, challenges and responsibilities.&nbsp;It is important therefore that you select professional advisers with the experience, expertise and track record you can trust to support your future development.</font></p><p>We have over 15 years of experience of academies and their predecessors, the City Technology Colleges.&nbsp;Our clients include almost 200 academies, free schools and University Technical Colleges, and range from standalone primary/secondary/all-through schools to large national federations.&nbsp;They embrace all the different types of academies – former City Technology Colleges, sponsored academies, local authority and independent school converters, and start up institutions.&nbsp;You can therefore have confidence that we will have relevant experience of the issues you are likely to face.</p><p><strong>Range of services</strong></p><p>Our breadth of specialist services is very wide and includes:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Assurance services, external financial statements and regularity audits</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Whole Government Accounts Returns and the Abbreviated Accounts Returns</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Accounting, management and financial reporting with the preparation of budgets and management accounts</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co