(134, 'en', 1, 91, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Further education and skills', '<p><strong>Working in partnership with the further education and skills sector</strong><br>&nbsp;<br>Baker Tilly has worked in partnership with the further education and skills sector for many years. We work with and advise many of the sector lead bodies including:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Key funding agencies – Skills Funding Agency and Education Funding Agency</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Government departments</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Association of Colleges</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">LSIS</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Sector Skills Councils</li></ul><p>We act for more than a quarter of further education and sixth form colleges as well as many training providers.&nbsp;Our training provider clients include not only charities and third sector bodies but also commercial organisations of many sizes.&nbsp;<br><br><strong>Supporting the sector</strong><br><br>We support the sector through leadership and guidance including:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Supporting research by participation and sponsorship, for example the review of governance aspects presented at the 2012 LSIS governance conference<