dth: 394.25px; \">strategic options reviews</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">project management</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">transactional support such as due diligence on potential partners</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">strategic planning</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">business process improvement</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">options appraisal</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">raising finance</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">recovery planning</li></ul><p>We also provide core compliance services such as:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">External and internal audit</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Tax planning and compliance – VAT, corporation tax and employment tax</li></ul><p><strong>Supporting clients</strong></p><p>Baker Tilly is a passionate supporter of the sector and for there to be continued improvement. Our support includes:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">free seminars and training on:<br>−&nbsp;technical financial matters<br>−&nbsp;taxation<br>−&nbsp;governance<br>−&nbsp;strategic matters&nbsp;<br>−&nbsp;key sector issues</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">commentary on emerging issues through board papers and briefings</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">presentations and training to governing bodies</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">ad hoc support and advice on a range of issues</li></ul>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(135, 'en', 1, 92, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Independent schools', '<p class=\"intro\">The competition independent schools face continues to be intense with many challenges for governors, heads and bursars. These include:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">the general regulatory and inspection burden;</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">economic downturns and the affordability of private education;</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">the difficulties in making surpluses from activities;</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">ability to fund capital developments;</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">competition from government funded academies;</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Teacher’s Pensions Scheme&nbsp;review and contribution rates causing financial pressures;</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">meeting the public benefit requirements.</li></ul><p>Baker Tilly has demonstrated a long term commitment to the independent schools sector over the last 20 years. We are currently the number two provider of audit services to independent schools&nbsp;<em>(source: CaritasData 2011/12)</em>&nbsp;and have consistently been one of the largest providers of audit services to the sector.<br><br>Clients benefit from our genuine interest and focus on the sector together with our understanding of the issues being faced. Our priority is to inform our clients, steering them through best practice and using our experience of the best management processes throughout the education and commercial sectors.<br><br><strong>Relevant experience</strong><br><br>Our education team has diverse and in depth experience across the education sector. We work closely with leading umbrella bodies such as ISBA and AGBIS and regularly contribute to their members’ support. We take the time to acquire real knowledge and understanding of your school by talking to the people who are responsible for day-to-day operations in order to deliver practical solutions that meet your specific needs. Furthermore, some of our education team are themselves governors, which enhances our practical understanding of the operational issues faced and informs the advice we give.<br><br>We are experienced in working with all types of schools - day/boarding, single sex/co-educational, preparatory/senior, charitable/proprietorial, standalone/consolidators.&nbsp;Our education team is based throughout the UK, so we are able to provide local support wherever your school is based.<br><br><strong>Advice and services</strong><br>Alongside our audit service, we also act for many schools on an advisory basis, providing advice in the following areas:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">VAT and corporation tax planning</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Mergers and acquisitions</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Governance and risk management</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Financial forecasting</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Schools in financial difficulties</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Schools requiring funding advice</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Review, selection and implementation of accounting and administration IT solutions</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Specialist insurance services</li></ul>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(136, 'en', 1, 93, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Public sector', '<p>The public sector manages more than 40% of the country\'s resources and cares for millions of citizens. Baker Tilly works to help organisations providing publicly-funded services to achieve their objectives in the most efficient way. From building infrastructure to promoting education, from care to family intervention - as well as new imperatives like dealing with climate change and achieving community cohesion moving up the agenda - there are many issues to tackle.</p><p>We can help those in the public sector and those managing publicly funded services to:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Get the best outcomes out of resources</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Develop performance measures around relevant outcomes</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Develop appropriate structures in which to develop those services</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Support organisational transition through merger, demerger and restructuring, including devolution to the third or private sectors</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Improve risk management approaches and link these to service effectiveness and funding</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Develop governance and scrutiny procedures and approaches to promote transparency and accountability</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Be assured about completeness and accuracy of information and about controls in systems</li></ul><p>We can help you establish your goals, then set out a path to achieving them.</p><p>To find out more talk to one of our specialists</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '');
