(137, 'en', 1, 94, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Social housing', '<p><font class=\"intro\" size=\"+0\"><font id=\"tmpPasteIE1312285780054\">Baker Tilly is a leader in its work with clients across the full spectrum of the social housing sector providing support and expertise through:</font></font></p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Compliance services including&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/audit/audit.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/audit/audit.aspx\">external and internal audit</a></li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \"><a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/tax/tax.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/tax/tax.aspx\">Tax planning and compliance</a>&nbsp;– VAT, corporation tax, PAYE, National Insurance</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \"><a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/finance/corporate-finance.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/finance/corporate-finance.aspx\">Corporate finance</a>&nbsp;including fund raising, mergers, acquisitions and disposals</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \"><a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/itadvisory/it-advisory.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/itadvisory/it-advisory.aspx\">IT strategies and effectiveness</a></li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \"><a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/publications/Social-impact.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/publications/Social-impact.aspx\">Measuring social impact</a>&nbsp;and social return on investment</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Assistance with efficiency agendas – Baker Tilly offers a nationwide<a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sectors/socialhousing/Pages/Back-office-benchmarking.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sectors/socialhousing/Pages/Back-office-benchmarking.aspx\">backoffice benchmarking programme</a></li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Assistance with process and procedures reengineering for cost saving and efficiency</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Working with regulatory bodies to provide seminars, workshops and other activities</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Advice on risk management and governance</li></ul><p><strong>Helping our clients with current sector issues</strong><br><br>We work closely with social housing organisations, including housing associations, registered social landlords and&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/publications/ALMO-Survey-2010.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/publications/ALMO-Survey-2010.aspx\">arms length management organisations (ALMOs)</a>&nbsp;to help understand and overcome the principal concerns and challenges currently facing the sector. These include:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">The repercussions and implications of the&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/publications/SHS-intro.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/publications/SHS-intro.aspx\">Comprehensive Spending Review</a></li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">The strictures placed on local authority funding and cuts in tenants’ benefit income</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Managing finance and delivering greater efficiencies</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Working with the Homes and Community Agency (HCA) from 2012</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Incorporating new accounting standards</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Rising tenant expectations</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Quantifying and maximising social impact</li></ul><p>Our approach is based on integrating our areas of specialist expertise and delivering value added through our national network of local offices. We enable our clients to keep up to date with internal and external pressures that are sweeping the sector.&nbsp;<br><br>Contact Baker Tilly\'s&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/SiteCollectionDocuments/Social%20housing/Social%20Housing%20Teamsheet%20-%202012.pdf\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/SiteCollectionDocuments/Social%20housing/Social%20Housing%20Teamsheet%20-%202012.pdf\">Social Housing team&nbsp;</a>to help guide you through these uncertain times.</p><h2>Our credentials</h2><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">No. 2 provider - of audit services to top 400 Associations</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">No. 1 provider - audit services to Housing Associations in Scotland</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Over 150 Social Housing clients</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">No. 1 provider - of audit services to the Arms-Length Management Organisations (ALMO) sector</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Wider not for profit experience - we are the number one adviser to the top 3,000 charities</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Advisors to regulatory bodies - we have specialists who have been appointed advisors to sector regulators and trades bodies e.g. members of the 2010 SORP working party and lead advisors to Scottish Housing Federation.</li></ul>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(138, 'en', 1, 95, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'null', '<p>As a Baker Tilly Azerbaijan we do have prominent experience collaborating with many banks in Azerbaijan. Actively we work with around 20 local and international banks operating in Azerbaijan. We do understand business needs and our professional team can support companies in the sector respectively. <br></p><p>The experts of Baker Tilly Azerbaijan have deep experience providing accounting and consulting services for banks and other financial institutions. We understand the challenges faced by executives in this highly regulated financial industry, including managing capital and liquidity, leveraging new technologies, improving processes, and meeting significant regulatory requirements.<br></p>', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null'),
(139, 'en', 1, 96, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Professional practices', '<p>Baker Tilly’s Professional Practice Group is a multi-disciplinary team of partners and managers dedicated to servicing all types of professional practice businesses. Our flair and sector expertise have helped us to achieve our position as one of the UK’s top providers of business services to the professions. We work with clients across the sector, including solicitors, architects,&nbsp;management consultants, surveyors and accountants.</p><p><strong>Helping our clients with current sector issues</strong></p><p>Like most businesses in the current economic climate, professional firms, both large and small, corporate or partnership, are facing numerous challenges. These include:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Complying with increased government regulation, both in the UK and internationally</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Identifying and adopting the appropriate strategy in uncertain market conditions</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Overcoming the constraints on working capital</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Getting the most from your workforce in a highly competitive employment market</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Mitigating the increased risk of fraud by employees</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Coping with departures or retirements of key individuals from the business</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Operating internationally in an effective and competitive manner</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Minimising exposure to the 50% tax rate for higher earners</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Responding to the changing nature of the buyer of services</li></ul><p><strong>Practical and relevant solutions to help your business succeed</strong></p><p>Our position in the professional practice marketplace enables us to not only influence technical and legislative developments for the good of our clients, but also to lead the way in identifying innovative and efficient solutions to their problems. What we can do:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Advising on changing regulations for professional firms, in particular the<a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sectors/professionalpractices/Pages/Legal-Services-Act.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sectors/professionalpractices/Pages/Legal-Services-Act.aspx\">Legal Services Act</a>&nbsp;and the risks and opportunities that arise from it</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Raising external debt or&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/finance/mergers-and-acquisitions-and-private-equity.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/finance/mergers-and-acquisitions-and-private-equity.aspx\">equity funding</a></li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Assisting with&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/finance/mergers-and-acquisitions-and-private-equity.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/finance/mergers-and-acquisitions-and-private-equity.aspx\">mergers, acquisitions</a>, disposals or public offers</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Advising on the most suitable business structure, whether corporate, LLP or hybrid</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Reviewing working capital management policies to ensure the optimum use of cash resources</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Creating&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/tax/employer-consulting-services.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/tax/employer-consulting-services.aspx\">effective remuneration strategies</a>&nbsp;to reward and incentivise key staff and owners</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Reviewing internal controls procedures and business processes to maximise efficiency and to deter fraud</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Advising on succession planning issues to ensure a smooth transition or exit</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Advising on the financial implications of operating in multiple jurisdictions with varying tax and regulatory landscapes</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Providing effective personal tax planning for partners, directors and employees</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Advising on the adoption of fee-charging models and arrangements to assist with client care</li></ul><p><strong>Industry expertise with international reach</strong></p><p>Our Professional Practice Group provides a complete range of specialist services to the professions in the UK and internationally, through the professional practice teams in the member firms of&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/international/baker-tilly-international.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/international/baker-tilly-international.aspx\">Baker Tilly International</a>. We assist our clients with:</p><ul style=\"line-height: normal; \"><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Regulatory compliance issues</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Audit, including adherence to Solicitors’ Accounts Rules (SAR)</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \"><a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/tax/corporate-tax.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/tax/corporate-tax.aspx\">Corporate and partnership tax planning and compliance</a>, both UK and international</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \"><a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/tax/vat-and-indirect-tax.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/tax/vat-and-indirect-tax.aspx\">VAT planning and compliance</a></li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Accounting support and preparation of financial statements</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \">Establishment of appropriate practice management systems</li><li style=\"background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); width: 394.25px; \"><a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/growth/Pages/risk-management.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/services/growth/Pages/risk-management.aspx\">Risk management</a></li></ul>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(140, 'en', 1, 97, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Legal Services Act', '<h2 class=\"line\" style=\"width: 394.25px; \">Legal Services Act index - an evolving insight into emerging trends</h2><p class=\"line\"><a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/SiteCollectionDocuments/Legal%20Services%20Act/Baker%20Tilly%20Legal%20Services%20Act%20forecast%20October%202010.pdf\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/SiteCollectionDocuments/Legal%20Services%20Act/Baker%20Tilly%20Legal%20Services%20Act%20forecast%20October%202010.pdf\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"ms-asset-icon\" border=\"0\" data-cke-saved-src=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/_layouts/IMAGES/icpdf.gif\" src=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/_layouts/IMAGES/icpdf.gif\">&nbsp;Read our Legal Services Act forecast October 2010</a><br><br><br><font class=\"intro\" size=\"+0\">Ever since Sir David Clementi’s final report paved the way for the enactment of the Legal Services Act 2007, Baker Tilly’s Professional Practices Group has been at the forefront of thinking on the impact of the regulation on legal service provision</font>.&nbsp;<br><br>We have combined our long experience of advising the legal profession with a broader knowledge of the investment and regulatory framework to deliver truly innovative thinking on Alternative Business Structures (ABSs) and the potential impact of external equity on the legal profession.<br><br>To enhance our thinking, one year ago we embarked on a project to gauge the movement over time in the attitudes and actions of legal firms in response to the opportunities and threats which will arise when the full provisions of the Legal Services Act come into play on 6 October 2011. We wanted to know whether this would create an appetite for activity or whether there would be apathy?<br><br><strong>Straightforward questions</strong><br><br>We monitored how thoughts developed over time by asking for responses to a series of 10 straightforward questions. We then used these results to monitor the movement in trends as events unfolded.<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><strong>A unique insight into developing trends</strong><br><br>This project was different to the many \'snapshot\' surveys that have been carried out recently because we have given an unparalleled insight into the shift of attitudes, trends and developments within the legal marketplace as time progressed.<br><br><strong>Regular feedback</strong><br><br>Our Legal Services Act webpage contains the results from both parts of our survey, and breaks down the results by size of firm to ensure relevance to you. This is enhanced by the commentary and insight in our Legal Services Act report so that you derive real value from this research.&nbsp;<br><br><strong>See the latest results</strong><br><br>We have presented our results in an ‘index’ format so that complex data can be interpreted easily, thus forming a basis for your own further thinking and actions.<br><br>If you would like to register to receive updates from our Professional Practices Group, including on our Legal Services Act survey please complete our&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/register-for-updates.aspx\" href=\"http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/register-for-updates.aspx\">register for updates form</a>.&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(141, 'en', 1, 98, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'null', '<p>The boom in investments in the real estate sector in Azerbaijan - most of it taking place in the capital city of Baku -- began approximately in last 10 years, with various international companies coming to the country to implement their grand real estate projects. Over time, new developments in the real estate sector paved the way for other infrastructure projects such as construction of new bridges, roads and road expansions to ease traffic congestion.<br></p><p> We work with a wide range of clients across the property and construction sector including investors, developers, construction firms, estate agents, surveyors and architects to understand and overcome the issues and challenges that they face such as: <br></p><ul><li>Compliance services including external and internal audit <br></li><li>Debt restructuring and related specialist tax advice <br></li><li>Tax planning and compliance – corporate income tax, VAT and etc. <br></li><li>Corporate finance including mergers, acquisitions, disposals and introductions to suitable business partners <br></li><li>Advice on cash management, planning and mitigating tax risks<br></li></ul>', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null'),
(142, 'en', 1, 99, 1, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'null', '<p>Retailing sector in Azerbaijan highly developed as consumer income levels increasing annually. Local currency stabilization, consumer confidence, increasing household spending boosted further growth of the sector. The main reasons for this performance were improved economic conditions in the country, increasing number of shopping centers, stores, outlets, brand boutiques and wider range of products available. <br></p><p>Through our work with clients across the retail sector we provide support and advice in: <br></p><ul><li>Strategic planning <br></li><li>Property/real estate <br></li><li>VAT and duty<br></li><li> Financial management and control <br></li><li>Corporate tax<br></li><li> Financing growth and succession<br></li><li> Employee remuneration and motivation <br></li><li>IT systems <br></li><li>Fraud detection and prevention<br></li><li> Corporate governance<br></li></ul>', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null'),
