(273, 'en', 1, 122, 1, '2015-01-14 16:49:20', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Audit Manager', '<p>Teymur Naghiyev started as an Audit Associate at “Baker Tilly Azerbaijan” from 2009 and later in 2011 he has been promoted to a Senior Associate. Currently he works as an Audit Manager responsible for oil and gas industry. Teymur has graduated from Azerbaijan State Economic University with bachelor degree. Later in 2008 he got his master’s degree from Yildiz Technical University. In August 2014 he has become a member of internationally recognized accounting association ACCA. Teymur has more than 6 years of professional experience in audit of various private and public companies in Azerbaijan.<br type=\"_moz\"></p>', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null'),
