(26, 'Andrew Martin Associates Limited', 'Andrew Martin Associates Limited', '<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; \">Baker Tilly&#39;s M&amp;A and Private Equity team has successfully completed the sale of Andrew Martin Associates (AMA) to The Capita Group Plc, the UK&#39;s leading outsourcing company.</span><br style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; \" />\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; \" />\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; \">AMA is a town planning and urban design consultancy that is best known for its promotion of large strategic residential developments through the UK planning system. Capita had been searching for a planning consultancy for some time, and the acquisition of AMA completes their suite of consultancy services to the strategic development sector.</span><br style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; \" />\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; \" />\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; \">Baker Tilly advised the shareholders throughout the transaction, led an international sale process during a challenging economic backdrop and delivered a deal with a strategic purchaser.</span><br style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; \" />\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; \">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; \" />\n<em style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; \">&quot;Baker Tilly got us a fan