(27, 'Pension Scheme Accounting', 'Pension Scheme Accounting', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; \">The production of the Annual Report and Financial Statements is compliance driven, but is also an opportunity for Trustees to demonstrate the adoption of best practice and good governance. This becomes ever more important as the complexity of investment portfolios increases.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; \">A medium sized pension fund with assets of &pound;250m had recently introduced greater complexity into its investment portfolio through the use of derivatives and hedge funds.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; \">Historically the annual financial statements had been produced in house and changes in the resources at the client&rsquo;s team meant that there was a lack of experience available.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; \">To assist, we undertook the accounts preparation exercise, working with the client regarding the supporting information required and utilising our disclosure checklists to ensure that all necessary disclosures were made. We also assisted in the development of the document by utilising our knowledge of best practice procedures seen when auditing other similar sized funds.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; \">With the deadline achieved and once the Trustees were comfortable with the final document, we liaised with their auditors, making a detailed working papers file available and responding to queries. At the conclusion of the audit process, few amendments were necessary and the Trustees were complemented on the quality of the financial statements received for audit purposes.</p>\n', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; \">The production of the Annual Report and Financial Statements is compliance driven, but is also an opportunity for Trustees to demonstrate the adoption of best practice and good governance. This becomes ever more important as the complexity of investment portfolios increases.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; \">A medium sized pension fund with assets of &pound;250m had recently introduced greater complexity into its investment portfolio through the use of derivatives and hedge funds.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; \">Historically the annual financial statements had been produced in house and changes in the resources at the client&rsquo;s team meant that there was a lack of experience available.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; \">To assist, we undertook the accounts preparation exercise, working with the client regarding the supporting information required and utilising our disclosure checklists to ensure that all necessary disclosures were made. We also assisted in the development of the document by utilising our knowledge of best practice procedures seen when auditing other similar sized funds.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; \">With the deadline achieved and once the Trustees were comfortable with the final document, we liaised with their auditors, making a detailed working papers file available and responding to queries. At the conclusion of the audit process, few amendments were necessary and the Trustees were complemented on the quality of the financial statements received for audit purposes.</p>\n', '<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; \">The production of the Annual Report and Financial Statements is compliance driven, but is also an opportunity for Trustees to demonstrate the adoption of best practice and good governance.</span></p>\n', '<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; \">The production of the Annual Report and Financial Statements is compliance driven, but is also an opportunity for Trustees to demonstrate the adoption of best practice and good governance.</span></p>\n', 0, 89, 1, '2013-03-13 04:36:45', 0, '', 0),
(28, 'Keep your garden safe', 'Keep your garden safe', '<p class=\"intro\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; line-height: 1.143; font-size: 1.16667em; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; \">Not many of us think about protecting our garden when we insure our house and contents.&nbsp;However, Sterling Insurance advise that according to a survey in 2010, almost one third of us spend more money on our gardens than any other area of our home.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; \">This makes us prime targets for burglars and the ABI estimates that 1 in 7 gardens will suffer a theft.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; \">The vast majority of burglaries from gardens are opportunistic and are of relatively low value although targeted thefts of garden machinery and ornaments can result in substantial claims. Even heavy items like stone benches and bronzes can be taken.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; \">It is important to ensure you have the right level of cover. BTIS are able to arrange policies that provide cover for outdoor items such as garden furniture, ornaments and children&rsquo;s play equipment as well as re-landscaping the garden and even replacing plants, trees and shrubs following a theft.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; \">Speak to your BTIS contact to make sure you have the right cover.</p>\n', '<p class=\"intro\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; line-height: 1.143; font-size: 1.16667em; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; \">Not many of us thin