(1, '2013-03-30 05:26:58', 'Baker Tilly Academy Forum Programme', 'Baker Tilly Academy Forum Programme', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">Our Academy Forums are facilitated by our local academy team who will bring in specialists from across all service lines to discuss specific relevant issues. The sessions will also provide you with the opportunity to network with your peers from other local academies. These events are designed for academy finance directors, finance managers, business managers or finance governors.</p>\n\n<h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.143em 0px; font-size: 1.1667em; line-height: 1.143; font-family: arial, sans-serif;\">Timings:</h3>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">08.00 - 08.30am Breakfast and networking<br />\n08.30 - 10.00am Topical discussion<br />\n10.00am Close and opportunity for further networking</p>\n\n<h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.143em 0px; font-size: 1.1667em; line-height: 1.143; font-family: arial, sans-serif;\">Venue</h3>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">Baker Tilly, 2 Whitehall Quay, Leeds, LS1 4HG</p>\n\n<h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.143em 0px; font-size: 1.1667em; line-height: 1.143; font-family: arial, sans-serif;\">Date</h3>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">Tuesday 15 January 2013<br />\nTuesday 23 April 2013<br />\nTuesday 18 June 2013</p>\n\n<h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.143em 0px; font-size: 1.1667em; line-height: 1.143; font-family: arial, sans-serif;\">Save the date</h3>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px