(3, '2013-03-30 05:34:34', 'Employer’s Year End – Northern Seminar Series', 'Employer’s Year End – Northern Seminar Series', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">The Government forces employers to act as tax collectors, loan recovery agents and state benefit distributors &ndash; all unpaid work and subject to penalties for non-compliance. In addition, penalties for late payment of in-year PAYE and the concept of &lsquo;reasonable care&rsquo; give HMRC further ways of extracting money from employers. The end of the 2012-13 tax year and the start of 2013-14 is a particularly challenging time as employers must make returns of last year&rsquo;s information whilst getting to grips with the additional responsibilities imposed by Real Time Information (RTI).</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><strong>The seminar will cover</strong>:</p>\n\n<ul style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0.666em 0px; width: 415px; float: left; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;\">\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Real Time Information (RTI) reporting</li>\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Tax year-end issues &ndash; P14, P35 and P11D problems</li>\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Pensions auto-enrolment and how it will affect your business</li>\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Our experience of the most expensive employment tax mistakes</li>\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Salary sacrifice: HMRC&rsquo;s current areas of concern</li>\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">An overview of the impact of the new statutory residence test for employers</li>\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Disguised remuneration &ndash; are we any the wiser two years on?</li>\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">A review of the Revenue&rsquo;s consultations and what they and the proposed General Anti-Abuse Rule signal for the future.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Who should attend?</strong><br />\nThe seminar is aimed at those responsible for payroll and staff remuneration and who need, whether directly or as supervisors, to keep up to date with PAYE, National Insurance and related areas.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Employer consulting team</strong><br />\nAt Baker Tilly we have a specialist group dedicated to providing advice and services on employer consulting matters. Our solutions can help not only to reduce the overall payroll costs, but also provide real incentives for key staff.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">We can work with you on all aspects of remuneration planning and tax risk management, including PAYE and NIC compliance. We&rsquo;ll help you avoid pitfalls in important areas such as:</p>\n\n<ul style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0.666em 0px; width: 415px; float: left; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;\">\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">reducing payroll costs</li>\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">share and share option schemes</li>\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">PAYE and NIC health checks</li>\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">dealing with HM Revenue &amp; Customs</li>\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">the Construction Industry Scheme</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">At the seminar you will have the opportunity to meet members of our employer consulting team and to discuss issues with our partners and staff.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Programme<br />\nTimings</strong><br />\n08.30am Registration and breakfast<br 