yers must make returns of last year&rsquo;s information whilst getting to grips with the additional responsibilities imposed by Real Time Information (RTI).</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 1.333em 0px; line-height: 1.333; width: 415px; height: auto; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><strong>The seminar will cover</strong>:</p>\n\n<ul style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0.666em 0px; width: 415px; float: left; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;\">\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Real Time Information (RTI) reporting</li>\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Tax year-end issues &ndash; P14, P35 and P11D problems</li>\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Pensions auto-enrolment and how it will affect your business</li>\n	<li style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.333; background-image: url(http://www.bakertilly.co.uk/sitecollectionimages/presentation/bullet-black.gif); list-style-type: none; clear: both; float: left; width: 394.25px; background-position: 0px 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Our experience of the most expensi