(15, 'Baker Tilly Roelfs Acquires Karl Berg GmbH', 'Baker Tilly Roelfs Acquires Karl Berg GmbH', 'Baker Tilly International member firm, Baker Tilly Roelfs, has completed the acquisition of Düsseldorf and Leipzig based auditing firm Karl Berg GmbH. The deal includes the affiliated companies Bedenbecker & Berg GmbH in Essen and KSR GmbH in Ennepetal, Germany.', 'Baker Tilly International member firm, Baker Tilly Roelfs, has completed the acquisition of Düsseldorf and Leipzig based auditing firm Karl Berg GmbH. The deal includes the affiliated companies Bedenbecker & Berg GmbH in Essen and KSR GmbH in Ennepetal, Germany.\n\nAs Ralf Gröning, spokesperson of the two-person management board of Baker Tilly Roelfs, explains: \"For us, the takeover of Karl Berg GmbH by Baker Tilly Roelfs means the continuation of a story of corporate success based on steady growth. This acquisition also represents a major gain for the managing partners of Karl Berg and for all its employees. They will now be entering a much broader and more international environment. But most of all – and this is the crucial factor – our joint clients will soon be enjoying the benefits of this new setup. Our primary focus will be on constantly maintaining a balance between new beginning and innovation on the one hand and continuity and total dependability on the other. All Karl Berg clients will of course continue to be served by the consultants with whom they are familiar and with the same high quality of service to which they have become accustomed. At the same time, they will benefit from a much broader knowledge base, from our interdisciplinary approach, in which auditors, lawyers, tax advisers and management consultants collaborate closely, and of course benefit from being a member of the Baker Tilly International network.\"\n\nIn order to ensure the smooth and speedy integration of Karl Berg GmbH, all personnel in Düsseldorf and Leipzig will be relocating to the premises of Baker Tilly Roelfs in the coming months. According to Dr Kai Alexander Behling, head of Karl Berg GmbH\'s auditing consultancy division in Düsseldorf: \"For us this step means a step into the future. Baker Tilly Roelfs will be providing us with an environment in which we as managing partners and also our staff can develop optimally. And for our clients it will mean the continuation of our successful collaboration – extending over several decades in some cases – as well as steady growth in terms of service quality and a more broadly based, international background.\"\n\n<p>Source: <a href=\"http://www.bakertillyinternational.com/\">Baker Tilly International</a></p>', 'Baker Tilly International member firm, Baker Tilly Roelfs, has completed the acquisition of Düsseldorf and Leipzig based auditing firm Karl Berg GmbH. The deal includes the affiliated companies Bedenbecker & Berg GmbH in Essen and KSR GmbH in Ennepetal, Germany.', 'Baker Tilly International member firm, Baker Tilly Roelfs, has completed the acquisition of Düsseldorf and Leipzig based auditing firm Karl Berg GmbH. The deal includes the affiliated companies Bedenbecker & Berg GmbH in Essen and KSR GmbH in Ennepetal, Germany.\n\nAs Ralf Gröning, spokesperson of the two-person management board of Baker Tilly Roelfs, explains: \"For us, the takeover of Karl Berg GmbH by Baker Tilly Roelfs means the continuation of a story of corporate success based on steady growth. This acquisition also represents a major gain for the managing partners of Karl Berg and for all its employees. They will now be entering a much broader and more international environment. But most of all – and this is the crucial factor – our joint clients will soon be enjoying the benefits of this new setup. Our primary focus will be on constantly maintaining a balance between new beginning and innovation on the one hand and continuity and total dependability on the other. All Karl Berg clients will of course continue to be served by the consultants with whom they are familiar and with the same high quality of service to which they have become accustomed. At the same time, they will benefit from a much broader knowledge base, from our interdisciplinary approach, in which auditors, lawyers, tax advisers and management consultants collaborate closely, and of course benefit from being a member of the Baker Tilly International network.\"\n\nIn order to ensure the smooth and speedy integration of Karl Berg GmbH, all personnel in Düsseldorf and Leipzig will be relocating to the premises of Baker Tilly Roelfs in the coming months. According to Dr Kai Alexander Behling, head of Karl Berg GmbH\'s auditing consultancy division in Düsseldorf: \"For us this step means a step into the future. Baker Tilly Roelfs will be providing us with an environment in which we as managing partners and also our staff can develop optimally. And for our clients it will mean the continuation of our successful collaboration – extending over several decades in some cases – as well as steady growth in terms of service quality and a more broadly based, international background.\"\n\n<p>Source: <a href=\"http://www.bakertillyinternational.com/\">Baker Tilly International</a></p>', '2014-02-28 06:59:27', '', 1, 0, 0, 9, 0, 0, 0),
(16, 'Baker Tilly Pitcher Partners Named Medium Accounting Firm of the Year', 'Baker Tilly Pitcher Partners Named Medium Accounting Firm of the Year', '<p>Baker Tilly Pitcher Partners in Melbourne has been named the Medium Accounting Firm of the Year at the Thomson Reuters Tax and Accounting Excellence Awards. The awards, announced in Sydney, aim to recognise excellence across firms and individuals in the expertise of tax and accounting throughout Australia.</p>\n', '<p>Baker Tilly Pitcher Partners in Melbourne has been named the Medium Accounting Firm of the Year at the Thomson Reuters Tax and Accounting Excellence Awards. The awards, announced in Sydney, aim to recognise excellence across firms and individuals in the expertise of tax and accounting throughout Australia.</p>\n\n<p>John Brazzale, managing partner of Baker Tilly Pitcher Partners in Melbourne, said that they were judged to be by far the most outstanding firm in their category. He added that this was achieved through demonstrating the ways in which they add value to clients, solve their problems innovatively, improve their competitive advantage and provide a positive working environment.</p>\n\n<p>In addition, the tax team was named as a finalist in the Indirect Tax Team of the Year category.</p>\n\n<p>Speaking of winning the award, Mr Brazzale said &ldquo;This award is another testament to the great work undertaken every single day by the staff and partners here &ndash; it demonstrates that we are the leading firm servicing the middle market.&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p>Source: <a href=\"http://www.bakertillyinternational.com/\">Baker Tilly International</a></p>', '<p>Baker Tilly Pitcher Partners in Melbourne has been named the Medium Accounting Firm of the Year at the Thomson Reuters Tax and Accounting Excellence Awards. The awards, announced in Sydney, aim to recognise excellence across firms and individuals in the expertise of tax and accounting throughout Australia.</p>\n', '<p>Baker Tilly Pitcher Partners in Melbourne has been named the Medium Accounting Firm of the Year at the Thomson Reuters Tax and Accounting Excellence Awards. The awards, announced in Sydney, aim to recognise excellence across firms and individuals in the expertise of tax and accounting throughout Australia.</p>\n\n<p>John Brazzale, managing partner of Baker Tilly Pitcher Partners in Melbourne, said that they were judged to be by far the most outstanding firm in their category. He added that this was achieved through demonstrating the ways in which they add value to clients, solve their problems innovatively, improve their competitive advantage and provide a positive working environment.</p>\n\n<p>In addition, the tax team was named as a finalist in the Indirect Tax Team of the Year category.</p>\n\n<p>Speaking of winning the award, Mr Brazzale said &ldquo;This award is another testament to the great work undertaken every single day by the staff and partners here &ndash; it demonstrates that we are the leading firm servicing the middle market.&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p>Source: <a href=\"http://www.bakertillyinternational.com/\">Baker Tilly International</a></p>\n', '2014-02-28 07:02:41', '', 1, 0, 0, 10, 0, 0, 0),
(17, '“Road from Baku to Warsaw: finance your business at Eastern Europe’s largest Capital Market”', '“Bakıdan Varşavaya: Biznesinizi Şərqi Avropanın ən böyük kapital bazarında maliyyələşdirin.”', '<p>On November 26, 2014 &ldquo;Baker Tilly Azerbaijan&rdquo;one of a leading audit and consulting firms together with &ldquo;Warsaw Stock Exchange&rdquo; (WSE) organized a seminar on &ldquo;Road from Baku to Warsaw: Finance your Business at Eastern Europe&rsquo;s largest Capital Market&rdquo; at Hilton Hotel Azerbaijan.</p>\n\n<p>In this regard the representatives of WSE Mrs. Beata Kacpyrzk and Mr. Mieczyslav Lazor as well as managing partner of &ldquo;Baker Tilly Ukraine&rdquo; Mr. Alexander Pochkun have been invited for joining the seminar.</p>\n\n<p>&ldquo;Warsaw Stock Exchange&rdquo; is the largest and fastest growing financial platform for issuing debt and equity instruments as well as making various investments in Eastern Europe. Significant number of largde institutional investors together with security issuing corporations are present in this market.&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p style=\"line-height: 20.7999992370605px;\">On November 26, 2014 &ldquo;Baker Tilly Azerbaijan&rdquo;one of a leading audit and consulting firms together with &ldquo;Warsaw Stock Exchange&rdquo; (WSE) organized a seminar on &ldquo;Road from Baku to Warsaw: Finance your Business at Eastern Europe&rsquo;s largest Capital Market&rdquo; at Hilton Hotel Azerbaijan.</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.7999992370605px;\">In this regard the representatives of WSE Mrs. Beata Kacpyrzk and Mr. Mieczyslav Lazor as well as managing partner of &ldquo;Baker Tilly Ukraine&rdquo; Mr. Alexander Pochkun have been invited for joining the seminar.</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.7999992370605px;\">&ldquo;Warsaw Stock Exchange&rdquo; is the largest and fastest growing financial platform for issuing debt and equity instruments as well as making various investments in Eastern Europe. Significant number of largde institutional investors together with security issuing corporations are present in this market.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Access to the capital markets for financing the projects is one of the major factors contributing to the successful development of the business in modern world.</p>\n\n<p>Pocession of the information about financial markets alongside with the opportunity for being part of these markets provides advantages for the participants in front of other companies and additionally creates positive envisonment for the business growth.</p>\n\n<p>This seminar is the beginning of the project which will be continued in 2015 aiming to inform the business audience of Azerbaijan as well as providing them access to one of the leading trade platforms of European Union.&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>Audit və konsaltinq sahəsində aparıcı şirkətlərdən biri olan &ldquo;Baker Tilly Azərbaycan&rdquo; şirkəti tərəfindən 26 noyabr 2014-c&uuml; il tarixində Hilton otelində Varşava Fond Birjası ilə birlikdə &ldquo;Road from Baku to Warsaw: Finance your Business at Eastern Europe&rsquo;s largest Capital Market&rdquo; m&ouml;vzusunda seminar ke&ccedil;irilmişdir.</p>\n\n<p>Seminarın aparılması &uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;n VFB-nin n&uuml;mayəndələri Biata Kasprişik və Mistislav Lazor, Baker Tilly Ukrayna şirkətinin idarəedici partnyoru Aleksandr Po&ccedil;kun dəvət edilmişlər.</p>\n\n<p>VFB maliyyə vəsaitlərinin cəlb edilməsində və investisiyaların yerləşdirilməsində Şərqi Avropada daha dinamik inkişaf edən və ən b&ouml;y&uuml;k ticarət platformalarından biridir. Burada bir &ccedil;ox iri həcmli investorlar və emitentlər təqdim olunmuşlar.</p>\n', '<p>M&uuml;asir d&uuml;nyada biznes layihələrinin maliyyələşdirilməsi &uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;n kapital bazarına &ccedil;ıxış, biznesin uğurlu inkişafı &uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;n əsas amillərdən biridir.</p>\n\n<p>Maliyyə bazarı haqqında məlumatın olması, eyni zamanda, həmin bazarın bir hissəsi olma imkanı, onun iştirak&ccedil;ılarına digərləri qarşısında &uuml;st&uuml;nl&uuml;k verməklə, biznesin inkişafı &uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;n daha əlverişli şərait yaradır.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Seminar Baker Tilly Azərbaycan şırkətinin Azərbaycan biznes-auditoriyasının məlumatlandırılması və Avropa İttifaqının aparıcı ticarət platformalarından birinə &ccedil;ıxışı &uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;n 2015-ci ildə davam etdiriləcək lahiyənin bir başlanğıcıdır.&nbsp;</p>\n', '2015-03-05 15:25:05', '', 1, 0, 0, 5, 15, 0, 0),
(18, 'Award Ceremony', 'Mükafatlandırma mərasimi', '<p><span style=\"line-height: 20.7999992370605px;\">Baker Tilly Azerbaijan held award ceremony for employees working for company already 5 years and more for their contributions and outstanding&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">work within the company. Samir Valiyev, Partner, marked that their achievements are a source of pride and inspiration for other employees.&nbsp; &ldquo;We are all delighted&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">to know that so many others appreciate your outstanding work as much as we do. It is always a pleasure to see great colleagues like you receiving the recognition&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">and applause you deserve so well&rdquo; &ndash; he mentioned.&nbsp;</span></p>\n', '<p><span style=\"line-height: 20.7999992370605px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.bakertilly.az/images/award5.jpg\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 150px; float: left; margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px;\" />Baker Tilly Azerbaijan held award ceremony for employees working for company already 5 years and more for their contributions and outstanding&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">work within the com</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">pany. Samir Vali</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">ye</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">v, Partner, marked that their achievements are a source of pride and inspiration for other employees.&nbsp; &ldquo;We are all </span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">delighted&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">to know that so many</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\"> ot</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">hers appreciate your outstanding work as much as we do. It is always a pleasure to see great colleagues like you receiving the recognition&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">and applause you deserve so well&rdquo; &ndash; he mentioned.&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"line-height: 20.7