(19, 'Charity for Street Children from Shelter', 'Charity for Street Children from Shelter', '<p>As part of its corporate social responsibility program Baker Tilly Azerbaijan organized charity for street children Shelter on June 11, 2015. This privately owned shelter provides support for needy children, both from the street and from the local neighborhood, who turned out sacrifice of aggression, violence and human trafficking.</p>\n\n<p>Baker Tilly arranged entertainment program, which made children and everyone in the shelter to feel fun atmosphere of the circus. Children will remember for a long time amazing program of pirates, with different competitions and games, singing and dancing, magician show with fantastic tricks, and bunnies coming out of hat and finally juggler show which made their day.</p>\n\n<p>After that children were provided with meal, juices and little presents.</p>\n\n<p>We are very pleased that we were able to touch the lives of these special children through this charity event.</p>\n', '<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"132\" src=\"http://www.bakertilly.az/images/shelter_for_children.jpg\" style=\"float: left; margin: 0px 8px 200px 0px;\" width=\"203\" />As part of its corporate social responsibility program Baker Tilly Azerbaijan organized charity for street children Shelter on June 11, 2015. This privately owned shelter provides support for needy children, both from the street and from the local neighborhood, who turned out sacrifice of aggression, violence and human trafficking.</p>\n\n<p>Baker Tilly arranged entertainment program, which made children and everyone in the shelter to feel fun atmosphere of the circus. Children will remember for a long time amazing program of pirates, with different competitions and games, singing and dancing, magician show with fantastic tricks, and bunnies coming out of hat and finally juggler show which made their day.</p>\n\n<p>After that children were provided with meal, juices and little presents.</p>\n\n<p>We a