(31, 'Global Annual Review 2012', 'Global Annual Review 2012', '<p>This report has been produced to enable our stakeholders to understand our global network. It explains how the network is run and our approach to quality assurance and client service. It also provides an overview of our members&#39; combined financial performance for the year to 30 June 2012.</p>\n\n<p>Source: <a href=\"http://www.bakertillyinternational.com/\">Baker Tilly International</a></p>\n', '<p>This report has been produced to enable our stakeholders to understand our global network. It explains how the network is run and our approach to quality assurance and client service. It also provides an overview of our members&#39; combined financial performance for the year to 30 June 2012.</p>\n\n<p>Source: <a href=\"http://www.bakertillyinternational.com/\">Baker Tilly International</a></p>\n', '<p>This report has been produced to enable our stakeholders to understand our global network. It explains how the network is run and our approach to quality assurance and client service. It also provides an overview of our members&#39; combined financial performance for the year to 30 June 2012.</p>\n', '<p>This report has been produced to enable our stakeholders to understand our global network. It explains how the network is run and our approach to quality assurance and client service. It also provides an overview of our members&#39; combined financial performance for the year to 30 June 2012.</p>\n', 1, '2014-02-28 06:36:37', 7, 1468, 0, 0, 1, 0, 'circle_of_pencils.jpg', 'a-world-of-opportunities.pdf'),
(32, 'Doing Business in Country Guides', 'Doing Business in Country Guides', '<p>The regulations governing doing business in another country can be complex. Our member firms work with clients to ensure that the pitfalls associated with expanding their operations into new territories are avoided. Our Doing Business in series provides background information to companies considering establishing and running a business in a particular country. For more information on doing business in another country, please speak to the relevant Baker Tilly International member firm.</p>\n\n<p>Source: <a href=\"http://www.bakertillyinternational.com/\">Baker Tilly International</a></p>', '<p>The regulations governing doing business in another country can be complex. Our member firms work with clients to ensure that the pitfalls associated with expanding their operations into new territories are avoided. Our Doing Business in series provides background information to companies considering establishing and running a business in a particular country. For more information on doing business in another country, please speak to the relevant Baker Tilly International member firm.</p>\n\n<p>Source: <a href=\"http://www.bakertillyinternational.com/\">Baker Tilly International</a></p>', '<p>The regulations governing doing business in another country can be complex. Our member firms work with clients to ensure that the pitfalls associated with expanding their operations into new territories are avoided.</p>\n', '<p>The regulations governing doing business in another country can be complex. Our member firms work with clients to ensure that the pitfalls associated with expanding their operations into new territories are avoided.</p>\n', 1, '2014-02-28 06:45:18', 8, 1658, 0, 0, 1, 0, 'executive_toy.jpg', 'united_kingdom.pdf'),
